node.title: Missing 14yo girl found
node.description: Police have found the 14-year-old girl in Canterbury who went missing on Saturday.
node.content:
["Police have found the 14-year-old girl in Canterbury who went missing.", "Isobelle had been missing from an address in the Southbridge, Selwyn District since Saturday.", "", "
\nPhoto: Supplied / NZ Police\n
", "She was last seen wearing brown cargo pants, a crop top, white Nike Airforce shoes and a blue Country Road shoulder bag.", "Police say she is safe and well."]
